{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDY5NDUzMDEw", "number": 3188, "title": "delete ctags temp files at the end of indexing", "bodyText": "This change should get rid of temporary files left around after killed Ctags processes.\nI verified that ctags creates the temporary files with names matching given pattern (on Linux):\n$ strace -e trace=openat ctags -f - opengrok-indexer/src/main/java/org/opengrok/indexer/analysis/LinkageType.java 2>&1 >/dev/null | grep tags\\.\n...\nopenat(AT_FDCWD, \"/tmp/tags.Z1MYq4\", O_RDWR|O_CREAT|O_EXCL, 0600) = 3\n\nand made sure the files are properly cleaned up at the end of the indexing.\nAlso created entries with name matching the pattern and having extra properties such as:\n\nnon-empty directory\nfile owned by root:root (while the indexer running as non-root user)\n\nto verify the behavior in case of failure.", "createdAt": "2020-08-18T12:03:18Z", "url": "https://github.com/oracle/opengrok/pull/3188", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "823830a9778f8e428b3070dec44dac7a14e38b90"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-08-20T14:36:10Z", "author": {"login": "vladak"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 11, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdAHV6HAH2gAyNDY5NDUzMDEwOjNkZDc1MGZjOGZkOGE5OTI4NGViNGVhZWIyYjdmZjQxYTVlODQyYTU=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdAtdrngFqTQ3MTQ1MzUzOQ==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "3dd750fc8fd8a99284eb4eaeb2b7ff41a5e842a5", "author": {"user": {"login": "vladak", "name": "Vladimir Kotal"}}, "url": "https://github.com/oracle/opengrok/commit/3dd750fc8fd8a99284eb4eaeb2b7ff41a5e842a5", "committedDate": "2020-08-18T13:50:30Z", "message": "delete ctags temp files at the end of indexing\n\nfixes #3183"}}, {"__typename": "HeadRefForcePushedEvent", "beforeCommit": {"oid": "472d76d7a00abd28421c8f6644d17b98e0ef8fff", "author": {"user": {"login": "vladak", "name": "Vladimir Kotal"}}, "url": "h